the device is running on Android Kitkat. But,

00:00:23.970 --> 00:00:28.039
again, this is the BETA version of the ROM
and according to me the stable version would

00:00:28.039 --> 00:00:30.900
definitely be running on android 5.0 lollipop.

00:00:30.900 --> 00:00:36.860
So, the company provided 4 pre installed themes
for the ROM which were the Black or the High

00:00:36.860 --> 00:00:43.410
Life theme, Light Pink or the Pink Blush theme,
The dark pink or the Rose theme and the Blue

00:00:43.410 --> 00:00:48.140
